; Coverage test for times.cc line 158, 160-161
; Exercise invalid date parsing (date that parses but reformats differently)
; Feb 30 gets caught at Boost.Date level. Let's try a date that
; passes parsing but fails the reformat check.

2024/02/29 Good Leap Year Date
    Expenses:Food            $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2023/02/29 Not a Leap Year
    Expenses:Food            $20.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 10:
While parsing transaction:
> 2023/02/29 Not a Leap Year
Error: Day of month is not valid for year
end test
